# 🚀 AI-Based Maze Solver Visualizer (10x10 Grid)

---

## 📌 Overview

This project is an interactive AI-powered maze solving visualizer built on a fixed 10x10 grid. It allows users to create or generate mazes and observe how different search algorithms explore and find the optimal path in real time. 

The application focuses on clarity, smooth animations, and algorithmic understanding, making it ideal for learning, demonstrations, and presentations.

It demonstrates and compares different pathfinding algorithms like:
* Breadth First Search (BFS)
* Depth First Search (DFS)
* A* Algorithm

---

## 🎯 Objective

The goal of this project is to:
* Enable users to design or generate mazes
* Apply AI search algorithms
* Visually understand how algorithms explore and solve the maze
* Compare performance of different algorithms

